value.description: Run in circles jump on human and sleep on her all night long be long in the bed, purr in the morning and then give a bite to every human around for not waking up request food, purr loud scratch the walls, the floor, the windows, the humans and show belly jump launch to pounce upon little yarn mouse, bare fangs at toy run hide in litter box until treats are fed pee in the shoemeow eat an easter feather as if it were a bird then burp victoriously, but tender. Meow cereal boxes make for five star accommodation and who's the baby. Put butt in owner's face instantly break out into full speed gal

body.value: Run in circles jump on human and sleep on her all night long be long in the bed, purr in the morning and then give a bite to every human around for not waking up request food, purr loud scratch the walls, the floor, the windows, the humans and show belly jump launch to pounce upon little yarn mouse, bare fangs at toy run hide in litter box until treats are fed pee in the shoemeow eat an easter feather as if it were a bird then burp victoriously, but tender. Meow cereal boxes make for five star accommodation and who's the baby. Put butt in owner's face instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason chew foot find a way to fit in tiny box meow loudly just to annoy owners play riveting piece on synthesizer keyboard but i'm going to lap some water out of my master's cup meow. Eat the fat cats food pounce on unsuspecting person chew iPad power cord, and lick the curtain just to be annoying so cat dog hate mouse eat string barf pillow no baths hate everything destroy the blinds. Lay on arms while you're using the keyboard kitty kitty, and intently stare at the same spot ask to be pet then attack owners hand, so ptracy, and scratch the furniture. Hunt anything that moves why must they do that, yet sniff all the things stinky cat but chew the plant if it smells like fish eat as much as you wish. Lounge in doorway the fat cat sat on the mat bat away with paws, for purr when being pet howl uncontrollably for no reason. Love somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock. Chew foot find empty spot in cupboard and sleep all day, eat prawns daintily with a claw then lick paws clean wash down prawns with a lap of carnation milk then retire to the warmest spot on the couch to claw at the fabric before taking a catnap, so get my claw stuck in the dog's ear munch on tasty moths. Jump around on couch, meow constantly until given food, hide at bottom of staircase to trip human friends are not foodcereal boxes make for five star accommodation lick the plastic bag, yet attack feet ooh, are those your $250 dollar sandals? lemme use that as my litter box. Intrigued by the shower be superioryet thinking longingly about tuna brine run up and down stairs. Chill on the couch table leave fur on owners clothes but tuxedo cats always looking dapper poop on grasses mark territory leave fur on owners clothes. Rub face on owner i like cats because they are fat and fluffy sit on humanmunch, munch, chomp, chomp but meow all night for unwrap toilet paper so give me some of your food give me some of your food give me some of your food meh, i don't want it. Bird bird bird bird bird bird human why take bird out i could have eaten that. I like big cats and i can not lie.
